<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.ico" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Share+Tech+Mono&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
      @font-face {
        font-family: 'Paragon';
        src: url('/fonts/Paragon-Regular.otf') format('opentype');
        font-weight: 400;
        font-style: normal;
      }
      @font-face {
        font-family: 'Paragon';
        src: url('/fonts/Paragonitalic-Regular.otf') format('opentype');
        font-weight: 400;
        font-style: italic;
      }
    </style>
    <title>OOMA — Manifesto</title>
    <style>
      *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; }

      html, body { margin: 0; padding: 0; }

      body {
        background-color: #141415;
        color: white;
        font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      /* ── Desktop: 2-column flex ── */
      .main-content {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: row;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 1265px;
        min-height: 100vh;
        padding: 80px 60px;
        gap: 30px;
      }

      .left {
        flex: 1;
        min-width: 0;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: space-between;
      }

      .right {
        flex: 1;
        min-width: 0;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
      }

      /* ── Logo ── */
      .logo-container {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: row;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 21px;
      }

      .logo { width: 96px; height: auto; }

      .company-name {
        font-family: 'Paragon', serif;
        font-size: 50px;
        font-weight: 400;
        color: white;
        line-height: 1;
      }

      /* ── Tagline ── */
      .studio-info {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 16px;
      }

      .section-title {
        font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
        font-size: 20px;
        margin: 0;
        color: white;
      }

      .section-description {
        font-family: 'Paragon', serif;
        font-size: 40px;
        font-weight: 400;
        margin: 0;
        color: white;
        line-height: 1.25;
        overflow-wrap: break-word;
      }

      /* ── Nav ── */
      .nav {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: row;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 20px;
      }

      .nav-links {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: row;
        gap: 20px;
      }

      .nav-link {
        font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
        font-size: 20px;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .nav-link.active { color: #FFE100; }
      .nav-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

      .contact-info {
        font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
        font-size: 20px;
        color: white;
      }

      /* ── Body text ── */
      .main-description {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 40px;
        overflow-wrap: break-word;
      }

      .text-block {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 12px;
      }

      .text-title {
        font-family: 'Paragon', serif;
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: 400;
        margin: 0;
        color: white;
        line-height: 1.2;
      }

      .text-body {
        font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
        font-size: 16px;
        margin: 0;
        color: white;
        line-height: 1.65;
      }

      .text-closing {
        font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
        font-size: 16px;
        margin: 0;
        color: white;
        line-height: 1.65;
      }

      /* ── Mobile ── */
      @media (max-width: 900px) {
        body { align-items: flex-start; }

        .main-content {
          flex-direction: column;
          min-height: auto;
          padding: 36px 24px;
          gap: 0;
        }

        /* Reorder: nav → logo → tagline → body */
        .nav   { order: 1; margin-bottom: 32px; }
        .logo-container { order: 2; margin-bottom: 32px; }
        .studio-info    { order: 3; margin-bottom: 32px; }
        .right          { order: 4; }

        .left {
          display: contents; /* flatten left children into main-content flow */
        }

        .section-description { font-size: 26px; }
        .company-name { font-size: 36px; }
      }

      @media (max-width: 480px) {
        .main-content { padding: 28px 20px; }
        .section-description { font-size: 22px; }
        .company-name { font-size: 26px; }
        .text-title { font-size: 22px; }
        .text-body, .text-closing, .section-title, .nav-link, .contact-info { font-size: 14px; }
        .logo { width: 64px; }
        .nav   { margin-bottom: 28px; }
        .logo-container { margin-bottom: 28px; }
        .studio-info    { margin-bottom: 28px; }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="main-content">
      <div class="left">
        <div class="logo-container">
          <img src="/assets/logo_white.png" alt="OOMA Logo" class="logo" />
          <span class="company-name">ooma</span>
        </div>
        <div class="studio-info">
          <p class="section-title">Our manifesto</p>
          <p class="section-description">AI characters are the next interface that gathers humans around.</p>
        </div>
        <nav class="nav">
          <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="/" class="nav-link">Home</a>
            <a href="/manifesto" class="nav-link active">Manifesto</a>
          </div>
          <span class="contact-info">contact@ooma.live</span>
        </nav>
      </div>

      <div class="right">
        <div class="main-description">
          <div class="text-block">
            <p class="text-title">How people will hang out in the post-AI world.</p>
            <p class="text-body">We are building the future social interface, one that is as entertaining as it is alive. The real magic happens when AI makes human-to-human moments richer, funnier, and more electric. A shared experience.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-block">
            <p class="text-title">The next AI characters interface is live, visual and shared.</p>
            <p class="text-body">Characters that perform and react in real time. Audiences that gather, argue, and build stories together.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-block">
            <p class="text-title">We are building the platform that makes all of it possible.</p>
            <p class="text-body">We are builders and artists working at the intersection of emotional intelligence, real-time interaction, and AI embodiment. We prototype fast, deploy in the wild, and learn from real social dynamics.</p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-closing">If this future excites you, we would love to hear from you.<br>— Alex, Kevin, and the OOMA team</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
